description: Commercial ACID Compliant Object Database for .NET, Mono, Xamarin MonoDroid, MonoTouch, Silverlight and Windows Phone 7. Features include LINQ index queries, lazy loading, paging, transactions, constraints, triggers, caching, BLOB, CLOB, Auto Identity Primary Keys, foreign key relationships, AES encryption, and compression.
releaseNotes: Kellerman Software announces a minor update to Ninja Database Pro; a database for Desktop, Silverlight, Windows Phone 7, Monodroid, Monotouch, and Mono. Performance has been increased when inserting thousands of records with an index. IsDirty is now set to false on load.
